AB  - To address the problems of the complex communication resource data types, long processing and transmission time, and low data coverage in the integration process, this paper designs an automatic integration method for multi-source communication data based on graph deep learning. First, according to the communication resource data attributes and interaction relationship to develop communication resource data classification standards, to achieve the same source data division to improve the integration efficiency. Then, we design the multi-source data-coding standard based on zero code, and associate the communication data types to improve the retrieval efficiency. Finally, the node matrix updating method based on graph convolution is proposed to extract the discrete data of nodes to achieve the integration of communication resources by combining multi-source data. The experiment proves that this data integration method can effectively improve the efficiency of multi-source communication data utilization with a data coverage rate as high as 85% and an integration time reduction of 56%.
