AB  - Distribution network construction is an important port for power grid companies to develop power grid. Under the background of the rapid development of energy Internet, the digital construction of distribution network can not only improve the quality of power supply, but also better serve the requirements of power grid and customers. Aiming at the problems of isolated data, lack of effective integration, lack of business data mining and lack of management and control means, this paper studies digitalization of distribution station area, digitalization of distribution terminal, intelligent distribution terminal access scheme, power supply service integration analysis, data fusion mining and grid three-dimensional command, and constructs a digital distribution operation and maintenance platform. The research results will improve the power supply service operation ability and efficiency, and improve the lean level of power supply service business management.
